#: ../../user/installation.rst:117
msgid "Installing MuJoCo (Optional)"
msgstr "安裝 MuJoCo（選擇性）"

#: ../../user/installation.rst:119
msgid ""
"First, go to the `mujoco-py`_ github page. Follow the installation "
"instructions in the README, which describe how to install the MuJoCo "
"physics engine and the mujoco-py package (which allows the use of MuJoCo "
"from Python)."
msgstr ""
"首先，前往 `mujoco-py`_ 的 GitHub 頁面。按照 README 中的安裝說明操作，"
"其中描述了如何安裝 MuJoCo 物理引擎和 mujoco-py 套件"
"（該套件允許從 Python 中使用 MuJoCo）。"

#: ../../user/installation.rst:123
msgid ""
"In order to use the MuJoCo simulator, you will need to get a `MuJoCo "
"license`_. Free 30-day licenses are available to anyone, and free 1-year "
"licenses are available to full-time students."
msgstr ""
"要使用 MuJoCo 模擬器，你需要取得 `MuJoCo license`_。任何人都可以獲得免費的 "
"30 天授權，全職學生則可以獲得免費的一年期授權。"

